Pipeline Flow:

Step 1: Data Collection
↓
Step 2: Data Preprocessing
↓
Step 3: Exploratory Data Analysis
↓
Step 4: Feature Engineering
↓
Step 5: Model Training
↓
Step 6: Model Evaluation
↓
Step 7: Prediction Output
↓
Step 8: Deployment (Optional)



Data Flow Explanation:

Raw data is loaded from CSV
Cleaned and transformed into usable format
Features engineered to capture volatility behavior
Model learns patterns from historical data
Predictions generated for unseen data



Pipeline Advantages:

Modular design
Easy to debug
Scalable for more cryptocurrencies
Reusable for other financial assets
